	Reorganizing (new dir lib/): move makefile fragments
	The new directory `lib', will contain all auxiliary files used by
	the testsuite.  In this commit, we move there Makefile fragments.

	* tests/CheckTestsList.am: Removed, moved to ...
	* lib/CheckTestsList.am: ... this.
	* tests/LocalCleanup.am: Removed, moved to...
	* lib/LocalCleanup.am: ... this.
	* tests/TestsEnvironment.am: Removed, moved to...
	* lib/TestsEnvironment.am: ... this.
	* tests/Makefile.am (include): Updated accordingly.
	* tests/SanityChecks/Makefile.am (include): Likewise.

	Bugfix in tests/SanityChecks/Makefile.am
	* tests/SanityChecks/Makefile.am: Removed the definition
	`$(XFAIL_TESTS) = $(RAT4_TESTSUITE_XFAIL_TESTS)'.  It was just
	cruft left when we did cut&paste from `tests/Makefile.am'.

	Separated test `switch-fail.test' in two test scripts
	* tests/switch-fail.test: Removed, separated into two new scripts...
	* tests/switch-fail-case-label-duplicated.test: ... this new script ...
	* tests/switch-fail-case-label-invalid.test: ... and this new script.
	* tests/Makefile.am (ALL_TESTS): Updated accordingly.

	Fixed/relaxed test `switch-fail.test'
	* tests/switch-fail.test: Removed part of the test, as that is now
	covered by the newly-added test `illegal-case-default.test'

